echo -ne "\n${cyan}~|${bold}[${cyan}+${cyan}]${end}${cyan}|${cyan}>${bold}${black} ~~~ ${end}${blue}Alongside with some other packages like: ${cyan}Polybar${blue},${cyan} Picom${blue},${cyan} ZHS${blue},${cyan} Sxhkd${blue},${cyan} Nvim${blue},${cyan} VS-Code${blue},${cyan} firefox_esr${blue},${cyan} Lsd${blue}..."
